      <title>markdown入门手册</title>
      <link href="2020/09/23/markdown/"/>
      <url>2020/09/23/markdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Markdown是一种纯文本格式的标记语言, 通过约定的语法使普通文本具备一定格式。 因此，只要支持Markdown的平台都可以达成同样的效果，让作者专心码字。<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" >Hexo</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span>已默认支持Markdown renderer, 用户只需要掌握Markdown语法即可。</p>        <h3 id="1-标题"   >          <a href="#1-标题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>1. 标题</h3>      <figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 这是一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 这是二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 这是三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 这是四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 这是五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 这是六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><a id="more"></a><p>对应效果分别如下:</p>        <h1 id="这是一级标题"   >          <a href="#这是一级标题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>这是一级标题</h1>              <h2 id="这是二级标题"   >          <a href="#这是二级标题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>这是二级标题</h2>              <h3 id="这是三级标题"   >          <a href="#这是三级标题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>这是三级标题</h3>              <h4 id="这是四级标题"   >          <a href="#这是四级标题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>这是四级标题</h4>              <h5 id="这是五级标题"   >          <a href="#这是五级标题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>这是五级标题</h5>              <h6 id="这是六级标题"   >          <a href="#这是六级标题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>这是六级标题</h6>              <h3 id="2-字体"   >          <a href="#2-字体" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>2. 字体</h3>      <figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**加粗**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*加粗&amp;斜体<span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="emphasis">~~删除线~~</span></span></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>对应效果分别如下:<br><strong>加粗</strong><br><em>斜体</em><br><strong><em>加粗&amp;斜体</em></strong><br><del>删除线</del></p>        <h3 id="3-块注释（blockquote）"   >          <a href="#3-块注释（blockquote）" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>3. 块注释（blockquote）</h3>      <p>方式一: </p><figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;代码块</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;代码块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>方式二:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% blockquote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">代码块</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endblockquote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>对应的效果分别如下:</p><blockquote><p>代码块</p></blockquote><blockquote></blockquote>        <h3 id="4-无序列表"   >          <a href="#4-无序列表" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>4. 无序列表</h3>      <p>无序列表用 - + * 任何一种都可以</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 列表内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>效果如下:</p><ul><li>列表内容</li><li>列表内容</li><li>列表内容</li></ul>        <h3 id="5-有序列表"   >          <a href="#5-有序列表" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>5. 有序列表</h3>      <figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 列表内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>效果如下:</p><ol><li>列表内容</li><li>列表内容</li><li>列表内容</li></ol>        <h3 id="6-有序列表"   >          <a href="#6-有序列表" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>6. 有序列表</h3>      <p>上一级和下一级之间敲三个空格即可</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 一级</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   *</span> 二级内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   *</span> 二级内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>效果如下:</p><ul><li>一级<ul><li>二级内容</li><li>二级内容</li></ul></li></ul>        <h3 id="6-超链接"   >          <a href="#6-超链接" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>6. 超链接</h3>      <p>![图片alt](图片地址 ‘’图片title’’) title可有可无</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">Hexo</span>](<span class="link">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片内联方式</span>](<span class="link">/assets/other/hexoLogo.png</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片引用</span>](<span class="link">https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/11456239?s=60&amp;v=4</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>对应效果分别如下:<br><span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" >Hexo</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span><br><img src="/assets/other/hexoLogo.png" alt="图片内联方式" title="内联图片"><br><img   src="https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/11456239?s=60&v=4" style=""  alt="图片引用"></p>        <h3 id="7-表格"   >          <a href="#7-表格" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>7. 表格</h3>      <figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">表头|表头|表头</span><br><span class="line">---|:--:|---:</span><br><span class="line">内容|内容|内容</span><br><span class="line">内容|内容|内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th align="center">表头</th><th align="center">表头</th><th align="center">表头</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr><tr><td align="center">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr></tbody></table></div><blockquote><p>备注: |之间的冒号表示对齐方式</p></blockquote>        <h3 id="代码和代码块"   >          <a href="#代码和代码块" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a>代码和代码块</h3>      <p>单行代码</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`单行代码`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>效果为: <code>单行代码</code></p><p>多行代码, 这里用到反转符号\:</p><blockquote><p>```多行代码```</p></blockquote><p>效果为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(&quot;hello world&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>]]></content>
      
      
